This directory contains the DTD for the Mathematical Markup Language (MathML)
Version 2.0 (Second Edition).  Its contents are essentially the same as
those of the MathML2 DTD tarball distributed by the W3C, except for the
correction of a minor bug in file isonum.ent (the original version is backed
up in isonum.ent.old).  The copyright of the MathML2 DTD belongs to the W3C:

Copyright 1998-2000 World Wide Web Consortium
   (Massachusetts Institute of Technology, Institut National de
    Recherche en Informatique et en Automatique, Keio University).
    All Rights Reserved.

